---
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>リスム | 空き家・古民家のリノベーション専門</title>
  <meta name="description" content="リスムは、空き家・古民家を価値ある住まいに再生するリノベーション専門サービスです。" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=M+PLUS+Rounded+1c:wght@300;400;500;700;800&family=Noto+Serif+JP:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --green: #2D6A4F;
      --green-l: #52B788;
      --green-d: #1B4332;
      --green-pale: #D8EFDF;
      --amber: #C87941;
      --amber-pale: #FBF0E4;
      --cream: #FDFAF5;
      --warm: #F5EFE6;
      --warm2: #EAE0D3;
      --text: #1E1E1E;
      --text-s: #6B6560;
      --border: #D8D0C6;
      --font: 'M PLUS Rounded 1c', 'Hiragino Maru Gothic ProN', sans-serif;
      --serif: 'Noto Serif JP', serif;
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { font-family: var(--font); background: var(--cream); color: var(--text); line-height: 1.8; }
    img { display: block; width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }

    /* ─── HEADER ─── */
    header {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      background: rgba(253,250,245,0.97); backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--text);
      height: 64px; padding: 0 40px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .logo { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--green-d); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: .06em; }
    .logo em { font-style: normal; color: var(--green-l); }
    nav { display: flex; gap: 28px; align-items: center; }
    nav a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--text-s); font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 500; transition: color .2s; }
    nav a:hover { color: var(--green); }
    .nav-btn {
      background: var(--green); color: #fff; padding: 9px 22px;
      border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 700; font-size: .85rem;
      text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid var(--text);
      box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 var(--text); transition: all .15s;
    }
    .nav-btn:hover { transform: translate(2px,2px); box-shadow: 1px 1px 0 var(--text); color: #fff; }

    /* ─── HERO ─── */
    .hero {
      margin-top: 64px; position: relative;
      height: calc(100vh - 64px); min-height: 560px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1480796927426-f609979314bd?w=1400&q=80') center/cover no-repeat;
    }
    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(27,67,50,.82) 0%, rgba(27,67,50,.55) 55%, rgba(27,67,50,.15) 100%);
    }
    .hero-inner {
      position: relative; z-index: 1;
      height: 100%; max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 56px;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    }
    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.18); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.45);
      color: #fff; font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700;
      padding: 5px 14px; border-radius: 100px; margin-bottom: 24px;
      letter-spacing: .1em; width: fit-content;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.6rem);
      color: #fff; line-height: 1.45; margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,.3);
    }
    .hero h1 em { font-style: normal; color: #74C69D; }
    .hero-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,.88); font-size: .97rem; max-width: 480px; margin-bottom: 40px; line-height: 1.9; }
    .hero-btns { display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-main {
      background: var(--amber); color: #fff;
      padding: 15px 38px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid var(--text);
      box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.4); transition: all .15s; letter-spacing: .04em;
    }
    .btn-main:hover { transform: translate(2px,2px); box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.4); }
    .btn-sub {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.12); color: #fff;
      padding: 15px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.6); transition: all .15s;
    }
    .btn-sub:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.22); }
    .hero-scroll {
      position: absolute; bottom: 32px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.6); font-size: .72rem; letter-spacing: .15em;
      text-align: center; z-index: 1;
    }
    .hero-scroll::after {
      content: ''; display: block; width: 1px; height: 40px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.4); margin: 8px auto 0;
    }

    /* ─── STATS ─── */
    .stats { background: var(--green-d); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--text); }
    .stats-inner {
      max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr);
    }
    .stat-item {
      padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);
    }
    .stat-item:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .stat-num {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--green-l); line-height: 1;
    }
    .stat-num span { font-size: 1.4rem; }
    .stat-label { color: rgba(255,255,255,.7); font-size: .8rem; margin-top: 6px; }

    /* ─── SECTION UTILS ─── */
    .divider { height: 2px; background: var(--text); }
    section { padding: 88px 40px; }
    .sec-inner { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .sec-label {
      font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .2em;
      color: var(--green-l); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .sec-title {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(1.5rem,2.8vw,2.2rem);
      color: var(--green-d); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .sec-desc { color: var(--text-s); font-size: .93rem; max-width: 520px; }
    .sec-head { margin-bottom: 52px; }
    .underline-deco {
      display: inline; background: linear-gradient(transparent 65%, rgba(82,183,136,.35) 65%);
    }

    /* ─── CONCERNS ─── */
    .concerns { background: var(--warm); }
    .concern-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 20px; }
    .concern-card {
      background: #fff; border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px 28px;
      box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--warm2); transition: transform .2s;
    }
    .concern-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .concern-card-icon { font-size: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .concern-card-num { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1rem; color: var(--green-l); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: .05em; }
    .concern-card-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green-d); margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .concern-card-body { font-size: .86rem; color: var(--text-s); line-height: 1.85; }

    /* ─── FEATURES ─── */
    .features { background: var(--cream); }
    .feat-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 20px; }
    .feat-card {
      background: #fff; border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 36px 28px;
      box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--warm2); transition: transform .2s;
    }
    .feat-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .feat-tag {
      display: inline-block; background: var(--green-pale); color: var(--green);
      font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 800; padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 18px; letter-spacing: .08em;
    }
    .feat-icon { font-size: 2.2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .feat-bar { width: 36px; height: 3px; background: var(--green-l); border-radius: 2px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .feat-title { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green-d); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .feat-body { font-size: .86rem; color: var(--text-s); line-height: 1.85; }

    /* ─── PROCESS ─── */
    .process { background: var(--warm); }
    .proc-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4,1fr); gap: 16px; position: relative; }
    .proc-grid::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute; top: 35px; left: 70px; right: 70px; height: 2px;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(to right, var(--green-l) 0,var(--green-l) 8px, transparent 8px, transparent 16px);
      z-index: 0;
    }
    .proc-step { text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .proc-num {
      width: 70px; height: 70px; border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--green); color: #fff; font-family: var(--serif);
      font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 700;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 18px;
      border: 2px solid var(--text); box-shadow: 3px 3px 0 var(--text);
    }
    .proc-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: .93rem; color: var(--green-d); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .proc-body { font-size: .82rem; color: var(--text-s); line-height: 1.8; }

    /* ─── CASES ─── */
    .cases { background: var(--cream); }
    .case-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 20px; }
    .case-card {
      border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden;
      border: 2px solid var(--border);
      box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--warm2); transition: transform .2s;
      background: #fff;
    }
    .case-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .case-img-wrap { height: 200px; overflow: hidden; }
    .case-tag {
      display: inline-block; background: var(--green-pale); color: var(--green);
      font-size: .7rem; font-weight: 800; padding: 3px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 8px; letter-spacing: .06em;
    }
    .case-body { padding: 22px 22px 24px; }
    .case-title { font-size: .97rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--green-d); margin-bottom: 8px; line-height: 1.6; }
    .case-desc { font-size: .83rem; color: var(--text-s); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .case-meta { display: flex; gap: 14px; font-size: .78rem; color: var(--text-s); }
    .case-meta strong { color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; }

    /* ─── VOICE ─── */
    .voice { background: var(--warm); }
    .voice-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3,1fr); gap: 20px; }
    .voice-card {
      background: #fff; border: 2px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px 26px;
      box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 var(--warm2);
    }
    .voice-mark { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 3.5rem; color: var(--green-pale); line-height: .8; margin-bottom: 6px; font-weight: 700; }
    .voice-stars { color: #F5A623; font-size: .95rem; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .voice-text { font-size: .87rem; color: var(--text); line-height: 1.9; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .voice-sep { height: 1px; background: var(--border); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .voice-author { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
    .voice-avatar {
      width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;
      background: var(--warm); border: 2px solid var(--border);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .voice-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: .87rem; }
    .voice-info { font-size: .75rem; color: var(--text-s); margin-top: 2px; }

    /* ─── FAQ ─── */
    .faq { background: var(--cream); }
    .faq-wrap { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .faq-item { border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border); padding: 26px 0; }
    .faq-q {
      font-weight: 700; font-size: .95rem; color: var(--green-d);
      display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 10px; line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .faq-q-badge {
      background: var(--green); color: #fff; font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 800;
      width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 6px; border: 1.5px solid var(--text);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px;
    }
    .faq-a { font-size: .87rem; color: var(--text-s); line-height: 1.9; padding-left: 36px; }

    /* ─── CTA ─── */
    .cta { background: var(--green-d); }
    .cta-inner {
      max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; padding: 0 40px;
    }
    .cta .sec-label { color: var(--green-l); }
    .cta .sec-title { color: #fff; text-align: center; }
    .cta-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,.75); font-size: .93rem; margin: 0 auto 36px; max-width: 500px; }
    .cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-cta-main {
      background: var(--amber); color: #fff;
      padding: 16px 44px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid #fff;
      box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.3); transition: all .15s; letter-spacing: .04em;
    }
    .btn-cta-main:hover { transform: translate(2px,2px); box-shadow: 2px 2px 0 rgba(0,0,0,.3); }
    .btn-cta-sub {
      background: transparent; color: #fff;
      padding: 16px 36px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem;
      text-decoration: none; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,.5); transition: all .15s;
    }
    .btn-cta-sub:hover { border-color: #fff; background: rgba(255,255,255,.08); }
    .cta-note { margin-top: 20px; font-size: .75rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); }

    /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
    footer {
      background: #111; color: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
      padding: 60px 40px 36px; border-top: 2px solid var(--text);
    }
    .footer-inner { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .footer-top {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 48px;
      padding-bottom: 48px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1); margin-bottom: 32px;
    }
    .footer-logo { font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.7rem; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .footer-logo em { font-style: normal; color: var(--green-l); }
    .footer-about { font-size: .82rem; line-height: 1.9; }
    .footer-col h4 { color: #fff; font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: .1em; }
    .footer-col ul { list-style: none; }
    .footer-col li { margin-bottom: 9px; }
    .footer-col a { color: rgba(255,255,255,.5); text-decoration: none; font-size: .82rem; transition: color .2s; }
    .footer-col a:hover { color: var(--green-l); }
    .footer-bottom { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: .75rem; }

    /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      header { padding: 0 20px; }
      nav { display: none; }
      .hero-inner { padding: 0 24px; }
      section { padding: 60px 24px; }
      .stats-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; }
      .stat-num { font-size: 1.8rem; }
      .concern-grid, .feat-grid, .case-grid, .voice-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .proc-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .proc-grid::before { display: none; }
      .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 28px; }
      .footer-bottom { flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<header>
  <a href="#" class="logo">リ<em>ス</em>ム</a>
  <nav>
    <a href="#concerns">お悩み</a>
    <a href="#features">特長</a>
    <a href="#process">流れ</a>
    <a href="#cases">実績</a>
    <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
    <a href="#contact" class="nav-btn">無料相談</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-badge">空き家・古民家リノベーション専門</div>
    <h1>眠っている家に、<br /><em>新しい命</em>を吹き込む</h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">リスムは、空き家・古民家を価値ある住まいに再生するリノベーション専門サービスです。地域に根ざした丁寧な提案で、あなたの想いを形にします。</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-main">無料相談を予約する →</a>
      <a href="#cases" class="btn-sub">施工事例を見る</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll">SCROLL</div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<div class="stats">
  <div class="stats-inner">
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">150<span>+</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">累計施工実績</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">98<span>%</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">顧客満足度</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item">
      <div class="stat-num">0<span>円</span></div>
      <div class="stat-label">初回相談料</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- CONCERNS -->
<section class="concerns" id="concerns">
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <div class="sec-label">Concerns</div>
      <h2 class="sec-title"><span class="underline-deco">こんなお悩みありませんか？</span></h2>
      <p class="sec-desc">空き家・古民家をお持ちの方のよくある3つの悩みに、リスムは一貫して応えます。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="concern-grid">
      <div class="concern-card">
        <div class="concern-card-icon">🏚️</div>
        <div class="concern-card-num">CONCERN 01</div>
        <div class="concern-card-title">誰も住まなくなった実家が放置されている</div>
        <p class="concern-card-body">老朽化や管理コストが気になるが、どこに相談すればいいかわからない。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="concern-card">
        <div class="concern-card-icon">🔑</div>
        <div class="concern-card-num">CONCERN 02</div>
        <div class="concern-card-title">古民家を活用したいけど費用が不安</div>
        <p class="concern-card-body">リノベーションに興味はあるが、古い建物は費用が高そうで踏み出せない。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="concern-card">
        <div class="concern-card-icon">📋</div>
        <div class="concern-card-num">CONCERN 03</div>
        <div class="concern-card-title">補助金や手続きが複雑で進められない</div>
        <p class="concern-card-body">補助金制度があると聞いたが申請方法が難しく、どこから手をつければいいかわからない。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <div class="sec-head">
      <div class="sec-label">Features</div>
      <h2 class="sec-title"><span class="underline-deco">リスムが選ばれる3つの理由</span></h2>
      <p class="sec-desc">空き家・古民家リノベーションに特化したプロが、ワンストップでサポートします。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-grid">
      <div class="feat-card">
        <div class="feat-tag">REASON 01</div>
        <div class="feat-icon">🏡</div>
        <div class="feat-bar"></div>
        <h3 class="feat-title">古民家・空き家に特化</h3>
        <p class="feat-body">一般的なリフォーム会社では断られがちな古民家・空き家も、豊富な経験と専門知識でしっかり対応。構造診断から竣工まで一貫してサポートします。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <div class="feat-tag">REASON 02</div>
        <div class="feat-icon">💬</div>
        <div class="feat-bar"></div>
        <h3 class="feat-title">ワンストップ相談窓口</h3>
        <p class="feat-body">設計・施工・資金調達・補助金申請まで、窓口はリスム一本。複数業者への連絡や調整の手間を省き、スムーズな進行を実現します。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feat-card">
        <div class="feat-tag">REASON 03</div>
        <div class="feat-icon">🌿</div>
        <div class="feat-bar"></div>
        <h3 class="feat-title">地域素材×現代デザイン</h3>
        <p class="feat-body">地元の木材や職人技を活かしながら、現代の暮らしに合ったデザインに再生。その土地の魅力を引き出した、唯一無二の住まいをご提案します。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="divider"></div>

<!-- PROCESS -->
<section class="process" id="process">
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <div class="sec-head">
